resources.string: O seu Pão de sempre... na sua porta!

LOREM IPSUM IS SIMPLY DUMY TEXT OF PRINTING AND TYPESETTING INDUSTRIES.LOREM IPSUM HAS BEEN THE INDUSTRIES DUMMY TEXT EVER SINCE 1500S.WHEN AN UNKNOWN PRINTER TOOK A GALLERY OF TYPE AND SRAMBLED IT TO MAKE A TYPE SPECIMEN BOOK IT HAS SURVIVED NOT ONLY FIVE CENTURIES.BUT ALSO THE LEAP INTO ELECTONIC TYPESETTING.REMAINING ESSENTIALLY UNCHANGED.
